SUMMARY:Work In Progress Art Club
DESCRIPTION:Our Work in Progress Art Club is the perfect place to unwind, connect with others, and bring your artistic visions to life. Bring a project, hang out in our studio space and enjoy access to our collection of art supplies for free. RSVP is welcome but not necessary. \nAs long as there is no inclement weather or conflicting events, join us every Wednesday from 5:00-7:00. \n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/work-in-progress-art-club/
ORGANIZER;CN=Second Story Studio:MAILTO:secondstorystudio.art@gmail.com
