SUMMARY:Variety Show at the Brown County Playhouse
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for a night of non-stop entertainment at the Brown County Playhouse! This one-of-a-kind Variety Show brings together the best in comedy, music, theater, and magic for an unforgettable evening under one roof.\nHeadliner Lloyd Wood leads a star-studded lineup that includes the mind-bending illusions of The Amazing Dennis, laughs from comedians Brian Smiley and Cole Peterson, and a dazzling performance from Songwriter Showdown 2025 winner Sami Riggs. The talented cast of Moon Over Buffalo takes the stage alongside the hilarious ventriloquist duo Jeff Goltz and Tony Bronchitis. Keeping the night rolling is your emcee Hondo, with Mary Ann Soll rounding out the fun as Card Girl.\nWhether you’re a fan of laughs, live music, theatrical flair, or a little bit of magic, this show has something for everyone. Don’t miss it!\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/variety-show-at-the-brown-county-playhouse/
