SUMMARY:Brown County Antique Machinery & Craft Show
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Brown County’s rich agricultural heritage at the Brown County Antique Machinery & Craft Show! Held at the Brown County 4-H Fairgrounds, this family-friendly event features a wide variety of antique tractors, engines, and vintage farm equipment on display. Enjoy live demonstrations, hands-on experiences, and a glimpse into the machinery that shaped generations of rural life. Visitors can also browse craft vendors, explore unique handmade goods, and soak in the nostalgic charm of this community tradition. It’s a fun and educational experience for all ages, bringing together history, craftsmanship, and small-town spirit.\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/brown-county-antique-machinery-craft-show/
