SUMMARY:Women’s Weekend
DESCRIPTION:Calling all women 18 and older! Come spend a long weekend at Waycross together. We’ll hike, work on a collaborative art project, pray together, and more! There will be space to reconnect—with yourself, friends – new and old, nature, and God – through engaging conversations and shared experiences. An optional personal retreat is available May 31-June 1st for extra time to unwind.\n\n\nMay 29-31, 2025 (optional extension to June 1st)\n\n\nCheck-in: 4-6pm\n\n\nCheck-out: Sunday 4pm, Monday 10am\n\n\n\n\nAges 18+\n\n\nProgram Rates\n\n\nAttendance cost is calculated during online registration, depending on your lodging selection. Rates are per person and include program fees, lodging and meals.\n\n\nConference Center – Single Occupancy (Friday-Sunday): $380 per person\n\n\nConference Center – Double Occupancy (Friday-Sunday): $310 per person\n\n\nConference Center – Single Occupancy (Friday-Monday): $555 per person\n\n\nConference Center – Double Occupancy (Friday-Monday): $450 per person\n\n\n\n\n\n\n
